Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後如果有需要幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還麻煩你多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼此彼此\N我們還那麼客氣幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些利用權勢\N貪圖私利的奸人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.68,0:02:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們神風隊要替天行道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.11,0:02:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！快…快來人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人 可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢…慢著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要多少錢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問了也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.38,0:02:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十五話\N火炎般暗殺集團\N神風隊橫行霸道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是人心惶惶啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.69,0:02:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說那個神風隊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近這個暗殺集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一一襲擊政府高官要員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過被殺的都有貪污嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以有很多人都認為神風隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為正義而戰的一隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.98,0:03:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不是一群以正義為名 而做壞事的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.18,0:03:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心派的活人劍\N才是正義之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.19,0:03:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！看不出禰彥\N偶爾也會說些像樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！偶爾兩個字就免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家來吃點心嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 小綾 小雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快來吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥吃點心嘍！我們快去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！好吃！好吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.24,0:03:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘烤的蕃薯\N真的好好吃耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀！真不好意思 惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰姑娘吃蕃薯的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是和蕃薯很配呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.62,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像不像傳說中的蕃薯姑娘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？什麼嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助你在笑什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！左之助在吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔！左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我直接闖進來真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？這不是老師嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹嘛慌慌張張的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我私塾的這個孩子\N突然喊肚子痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.39,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得左之你有醫生朋友\N所以才趕緊帶他來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是玄齊醫生剛好不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺因公事出遠門去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在家喲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰姑娘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你準備一床棉被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.28,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心麻煩你去燒鍋熱水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.28,0:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 這位姑娘是醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！女醫生啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個性我不敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是她的醫術 我敢給你擔保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.26,0:05:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話少說 快幫我抱這孩子躺下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少一副命令的口氣 這八婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！不可以吵架 左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看啊！左之八成喜歡惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人在喃喃什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！帶進房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是感激不盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像吃壞肚子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經不礙事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍微睡一下就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是幫了大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不知要如何感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師我也幫你看看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.89,0:05:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師你的臉色很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我啊！我只是吃得不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在是因為太窮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了！太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師是私塾的老師嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他和我一樣住在長屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本是位武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知為何流落到長屋\N這事我也沒問過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果在以前就是流浪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他其實每日受雇幹活\N過著清貧的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還開了家不收學費的私塾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教附近的孩子讀書寫字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好偉大喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只覺得那老師好像在哪見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事沒事 可能是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.87,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是要好身手的刺客嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.04,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後對方為了自保都警備森嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要像之前這麼順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要加強神風隊的戰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有人選？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.62,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像過去斬人拔刀齊\N轟動京城那樣的刺客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了明治這時代\N這要求會不會太過份？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有想到一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔！真有這樣的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他身手沒退步的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起拔刀齊有過之而無不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那好！就交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 今天晚上吃什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拔了顆好蘿蔔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山芋拿來煮湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再炒個青菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會蠻豐盛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是昨天那位老師嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！老師 你也到旁邊休息一下嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛那麼拚命呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再一會就可告一段落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然跟左之助說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那混蛋想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不凡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見！佐佐木老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是神東馬嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下我放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的身手還是跟以前一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我們很快會再見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.58,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你看到了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那老師的攻擊快得看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.49,0:10:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是火野派一刀流\N登峰造極的[紫電太刀]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫電太刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.37,0:10:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓對手防守不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.14,0:10:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃電般刺穿對手的暗殺劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.71,0:10:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那老師到底是何許人物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京城曾和他交手過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？劍心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.66,0:11:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時對手是一個名叫\N新撰組的恐怖劍客集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來才知道 他是\N京都捕組組長佐佐木平八郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.67,0:11:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那老師是新撰組的劍客嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是人不可貌相啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚一個人喝真沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒跟老師喝一杯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那夥人是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.88,0:12:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐佐木老師 前幾天失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚叫我出來是為了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在學火野一刀流時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已是師父級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時我還只是初出茅廬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才一陣子不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的劍術已經這麼高明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這期間你殺了多少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先前你使太刀的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是殺人不眨眼的劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍本來就是用來斬人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的劍不也是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.88,0:12:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想不想再讓拿起劍 暢快地斬人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指暗殺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.09,0:12:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新政府輕視我們武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.59,0:12:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府官員都是利用權勢\N中飽私囊的奸人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.89,0:12:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打擊這種腐敗的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有暗殺才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就能改變世界嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會用這把劍改變給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該不想就這樣終老一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要再登上光明的舞台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.71,0:13:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人者都光明不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可能再做這種傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我已棄劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.52,0:13:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私塾的孩子們\N才是我珍視的寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且藉著教育這些孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.13,0:13:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能洗清我殺人無數的罪過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬 我們應該不會再見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.94,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們神風隊要的東西\N是絕對逃不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何 都要你加入我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:14:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來和劍心一樣\N對老師真要刮目相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那後來老師怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.71,0:14:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他斷然拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那夥人絕非善類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來不知會做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也來幫忙一下嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別叫他了 惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.19,0:14:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫左之助幫忙打掃\N待會下大雨就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了！才剛到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來！玄齊醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.51,0:14:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都還好吧？\N我最擔心你們兩個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你們這麼有精神就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺！ 你真的那麼擔心我們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是我的寶貝呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已棄劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.89,0:15:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在私塾的孩子們\N才是我珍視的寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孩子們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？那傢伙匆匆忙忙地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.34,0:15:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道 一定是不打掃 怕被爺爺罵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論用什麼手段\N都要讓你加入我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我寫好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔！寫得真快 菊松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪 拿來我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經決定好下個目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要不要跟我走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.47,0:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菊松！發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師跟著一個奇怪的人走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？老師往哪邊走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往品川那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.48,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！那混蛋果然找到這堥茪F
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北村總議長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們替天行道來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是神風隊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.73,0:17:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是神風隊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！那夥人在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前面的小路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐佐木老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經不能回頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是無法捨棄劍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.67,0:18:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左…左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私塾老師怎麼可以拿那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿孩子們相要脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這沒良心的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.09,0:18:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相樂左之助決不原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著！左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.86,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔別發抖了 快站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能幫你到這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的性命自己顧吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.12,0:18:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢阻礙我神風隊的行動 好大的膽量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.44,0:19:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對沒武器的人拔劍\N不覺得可恥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.14,0:19:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的對手應該是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.85,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿那逆刃刀 真是笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有趣！你們都別出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了！紫電太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.39,0:19:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！那劍法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等沒人打擾時\N我們再一比高下吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.60,0:20:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時我的劍 一定會刺穿你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.65,0:20:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男的劍法和老師你的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.13,0:20:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我也差點就送命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年過得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是當時的斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.94,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我捨棄了過去的名字來東京的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像你捨棄你的劍一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧！老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和劍心不會讓人來破壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師的手已不是握劍的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.59,0:21:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是教孩子讀書的重要的手
